{"tid":1386790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳]關於藏有攻擊性武器，一定要知","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T10:07:20.000Z","uid":42093,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bedde4e57fee02f3cd6c6695eb2fb52bcba6c202","tid":1386790,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:55:48.000Z","msg":"《公安條例》 第33條 在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n今日就有四個義士因為呢條罪而無法保釋。<br />\n<br />\n發夢過來人話你聽，呢條罪係一條非常容易＋非常嚴重既罪行，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">襲警都未必一定坐，但呢條坐硬，係無得社會服務令、無緩刑既罪</span></span>。少至一個月，最多兩年。<br />\n<br />\n咩野係藏有攻擊性武器？其實只要無合理解釋下，拎任何適合傷害他人的物品，即係差唔多所有物品，只要有攻擊意圖，都入到罪。就算答自衛/防身，入罪機會率都好高，因為香港法例香港人無權搵武器傍身，自衛，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多案例係無人受傷既情況下，答自衛/防身最後都有入罪&amp;監禁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n合理解釋係咩？裝修工人帶工具出街、送貨工人帶工作用既界刀，呢D係合理解釋，但都會睇環境證據。今時今日，大多都會拉左你告左先，而個官都會唔俾你保釋，扔你入荔枝角一個月先上第二庭，就算你真係有合理解釋，都要睇個官點判，有案例都要去到上訴先還你清白，分分鐘坐完先上訴成功，一拉分分鐘錯過全個運動、未計金錢，絕對唔值。<br />\n<br />\n惡法就點都係惡法，而家D狗經常搜身、查身份證，絕對會用呢條惡法去打擊示威者，一定要絕對小心，當然有人覺得，搵到合理理由就會無事，但以班狗既做法，盡量避免進入司法程序，唔好俾籍口佢地拉你先係最重要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能好多地方講得未夠清楚，有問題會盡答。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地來港青年隨身帶摺刀囚2星期<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160520/s00001/1463739269573/內地來港青年隨身帶摺刀囚2星期-官-望被告學懂香港法律-信任警會保護市民\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160520%2Fs00001%2F1463739269573%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%E5%B8%B6%E6%91%BA%E5%88%80%E5%9B%9A2%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F-%E5%AE%98-%E6%9C%9B%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E5%AD%B8%E6%87%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B-%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=31b2e024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160520%2Fs00001%2F1463739269573%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%E5%B8%B6%E6%91%BA%E5%88%80%E5%9B%9A2%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F-%E5%AE%98-%E6%9C%9B%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E5%AD%B8%E6%87%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B-%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91&h=51688374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160520/s00001/1463739269573/內地來港青年隨身帶摺刀囚2星期-官-望被告學懂香港法律-信任警會保護市民</a><br />\n<br />\n【法律掃盲】究竟帶𠝹刀出街犯唔犯法？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/30/163142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F163142&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=fd9ba988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/30/163142</a>"},{"pid":"11f7a06e49881df352827dbec10ba2bcb0954027","tid":1386790,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推上去"},{"pid":"e5640a6bd341cc3a34973f00c83071cdaa48fbe8","tid":1386790,"uid":96945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c19e63a7fda188cb7f6b65716cc030352650fc61","tid":1386790,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b285ba98bc343bc3def515c6c47f3d01f56069e4","tid":1386790,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a643f137f284c0c4cbf642acd454a490c01e10","tid":1386790,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0